<item>
            <title>[LU-18780] Running &quot;lfs quota -a -u /lustre&quot; Simultaneously Causes the lfs quota to Hang</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18780</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running &apos;lfs quota -a -u/-g/-p /lustre&apos; simultaneously causes the commands to hang. &lt;br/&gt;
They said that the commands were run simultaneously by cron at 16:00.&lt;/p&gt;

